| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2052 — Recovery Inhibition (interlock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f4a6ebd2-c199-5fe2-8501-f513ccf2b5be"
